{"tid":958873,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尼姑操兵你見過未？ 對五星旗、毛像敬禮","createTime":"2018-12-28T07:28:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T07:49:43.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"00d24afa9a92dfa7bbe6fe56fba4b8af9682a05b","tid":958873,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T07:28:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181228/large/1545975289_76e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181228%2Flarge%2F1545975289_76e4.jpg&h=19f382fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181228/large/1545975289_c470.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181228%2Flarge%2F1545975289_c470.jpg&h=0d8f9b6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12月26日是中共前領導人毛澤東誕辰125周年紀念日。內地甚至有說法稱，12月26日才是中國人的聖誕節。網上近日流傳一段影片，可見本應以佛祖為尊的尼姑操兵上台，向五星旗、毛澤東像敬禮。<br />\n<br />\n影片的拍攝地點及時間不詳。影片可見，身穿僧服的光頭尼姑擺手踏腳，整齊站列步向台前，有人拿着紅底黃字的「大佛頂首楞嚴經」旗幟，分別站在台的左右方；舞台的壁佈則是背後畫上黃光的毛澤東像；兩名貌似輩分較高的尼姑和和尚則上台，將本來合十的「阿彌陀佛」手勢，改成對五星旗、毛像舉起敬禮手勢；背景奏樂亦相當激昂，與佛家清淨的感覺截然不同。<br />\n<br />\n今年4月起，中央宣稱宗教要「中國化」，內地寺廟就相繼掛上五星旗、舉行升旗禮，未知影片中尼姑所行，是否也是配合國家政策的措舉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181228/59078889\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181228%2F59078889&d=CSuYvDQdr8UAJTJOepUIsLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=32bea60a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181228%2F59078889&h=8341c30e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181228/59078889</a>"},{"pid":"13dbeb7602f3497cd9d896e6e7b1660e9ca1ea06","tid":958873,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T07:29:05.000Z","msg":"尼姑也愛國<img src=\"/assets/fac